original: Ahlstrand, Isak Anton Ragnar, kassör, Halmstad, f. 5/12/00 i Karlskrona av Alfred A. o. Tekla Ahl-strand-Hjortsberg. G. 32 m. Gudrun Frick. Barm Krister f. 43. — Tekn. :sk. 20, handisk. 24. Anst. i Skand. Banken 25-30, kassör i Östra Bryggeri A-B i Halmstad S’ed. 30. Medl. av Frimurarorden.
translated: Ahlstrand, Isak Anton Ragnar, treasurer, Halmstad, b. 5/12/00 in Karlskrona to Alfred A. and Tekla Ahlstrand-Hjortsberg. Married in 1932 to Gudrun Frick. Son Krister born in 1943. Technical school 1920, commercial school 1924. Employed in Skand. Banken from 1925-1930, treasurer in Östra Bryggeri A-B in Halmstad since 1930. Member of the Freemason order.
